<div class="chapter">
<h2 class="nobreak" id="FOREWORD">FOREWORD</h2>
</div>

<p class="drop-cap-text"><span class="smcap1">The</span> matter contained in this book
originally appeared, in substantially
the same form, as a series of articles in
our monthly publication “Plymouth
Products.” The story aimed to make
better known an industry previously little
understood and thereby to advance the
cause of good rope.</p>

<p>First and last this “Story of Rope”
has had many interested and responsive
readers. Encouraged by the large numbers
of requests for it which continually
come to us, we are now led to publish it
anew and with the hope that in its present
improved form it will still further
fulfill its original purpose.</p>

<p class="right">
<span class="smcap">Plymouth Cordage Company</span>
</p>

