  <img alt=" " height="2652" src="images/i_076.jpg" width="4215" id="id-5653058712130965537">
  <figcaption class="caption">PLATFORM AND APPARATUS FOR STORAGE AND HANDLING OF TAR SUPPLY,<br>
PLYMOUTH CORDAGE COMPANY
</figcaption></figure>
